            <div class="inspire-right-in">
               <h1>Our Story</h1>
               <p>Sola Salon Studios was founded in 2004 with the dream of doing more than designing beautiful, move-in-ready salon studios. We set out to build a thriving community where independent beauty professionals could create a life and career they loved. Throughout the years, Sola has become more than just another salon suites rental business; we are an all-encompassing independent salon business solution. Our leadership team drives constant innovation for the on-site studio experience as well as providing cutting-edge technology and ongoing educational resources to the Sola community. Over the past 15 years, the original Sola dream has blossomed into a worldwide movement and a thriving, diverse and welcoming community of more than 18,000 independent salon professionals across 600+ locations in the United States, Canada and Brazil. We are continuing to grow and excited to meet motivated, passionate franchisees to join our high-powered and sophisticated roster on the journey to success. Sola Salon Studios is a brand you can feel proud to be a part of.</p>
